## Ingredients

- [ ] 1.5 tsp ground cumin
- [ ] 1 tsp ground cardamom
- [ ] 1 tsp ground coriander
- [ ] 3/4 tsp ground black pepper
- [ ] 3/4 tsp turmeric
- [ ] 1/2 tsp ground cinnamon
- [ ] 1/4 tsp ground cloves
- [ ] 1/4 tsp ground nutmeg

## Notes

- Makes 2 Tbsp
